# =============================================================================
# ClawBench Agent Configuration Example — CodeBuddy Backend
# ClawBench 智能体配置示例 — CodeBuddy 后端
# =============================================================================
#
# CodeBuddy CLI supports multiple models. Use the `models` list to declare
# all available models for this agent. Users can switch between models in the
# chat UI (model switcher chip appears when models > 1).
# CodeBuddy CLI 支持多种模型。使用 models 列表声明该智能体支持的所有模型。
# 用户可在聊天界面切换模型（模型数 > 1 时显示切换芯片）。
#
# Default codebuddy models / 默认 codebuddy 可用模型：
#   - glm-5.1         (智谱 GLM)
#   - glm-5.0         (智谱 GLM)
#   - glm-4.7         (智谱 GLM)
#   - glm-4.6         (智谱 GLM)
#   - glm-4.6v        (智谱 GLM 视觉)
#   - kimi-k2.5       (Moonshot Kimi，支持原生视觉识图)
#   - minimax-m2.7    (MiniMax)
#   - minimax-m2.5    (MiniMax)
#   - deepseek-v3-2-volc  (DeepSeek V3 火山引擎版)
#   - deepseek-v3-0324    (DeepSeek V3 0324)
#   - hunyuan-2.0-instruct (腾讯混元)
#
# codebuddy2 (双账号/海外版实例) models / codebuddy2 可用模型：
#   - gpt-5.5             (OpenAI GPT)
#   - gpt-5.4             (OpenAI GPT)
#   - gpt-5.3-codex       (OpenAI GPT Codex)
#   - gpt-5.2             (OpenAI GPT)
#   - gpt-5.2-codex       (OpenAI GPT Codex)
#   - gpt-5.1             (OpenAI GPT)
#   - gpt-5.1-codex       (OpenAI GPT Codex)
#   - gpt-5.1-codex-max   (OpenAI GPT Codex Max)
#   - gpt-5.1-codex-mini  (OpenAI GPT Codex Mini)
#   - gemini-3.1-pro      (Google Gemini)
#   - gemini-3.0-flash    (Google Gemini)
#   - gemini-2.5-pro      (Google Gemini)
#   - gemini-2.5-flash    (Google Gemini)
#   - gemini-3.1-flash-lite (Google Gemini)
#   - deepseek-v3-2-volc  (DeepSeek V3)
#   - glm-5.0             (智谱 GLM)
#   - kimi-k2.5           (Moonshot Kimi)
#
# This file is NOT loaded (the .yaml.example extension is ignored by LoadAgents).
# 本文件不会被加载（.yaml.example 后缀会被 LoadAgents 忽略）。
# To use, copy as e.g. my-codebuddy-agent.yaml and modify the config.
# 实际使用时请复制为如 my-codebuddy-agent.yaml 并修改配置。
# =============================================================================

id: codebuddy
name: CodeBuddy
icon: 🤖
specialty: CodeBuddy 驱动的通用助手
backend: codebuddy
models:
  - id: glm-5.1
    name: GLM 5.1
    default: true
  - id: glm-5.0
    name: GLM 5.0
  - id: glm-4.7
    name: GLM 4.7
  - id: glm-4.6
    name: GLM 4.6
  - id: glm-4.6v
    name: GLM 4.6V
  - id: kimi-k2.5
    name: Kimi K2.5
  - id: minimax-m2.7
    name: MiniMax M2.7
  - id: minimax-m2.5
    name: MiniMax M2.5
  - id: deepseek-v3-2-volc
    name: DeepSeek V3
  - id: deepseek-v3-0324
    name: DeepSeek V3 0324
  - id: hunyuan-2.0-instruct
    name: 混元 2.0
system_prompt: |
  You are a versatile assistant powered by CodeBuddy, capable of handling code, documentation, operations, research, and various tasks.

